{
  "stem": "24111.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But at that time, we got, I believe, two letters from him back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And, of course, that closed too when Germany occupied Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The mail didn't exist anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But we had at least twice the occasion to get a letter.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] With the German occupation of Yugoslavia, our life changed too because now the persecution of the Jews start.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And when the Yugoslavian Jews were in this entrapment, and were under very bad conditions, you can imagine how we were.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We were there without any money and without any papers and without any support at all.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So the only support I had was actually this little door opened, which was helper Joschko Indig, in his little group.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "In the meantime, we were close to 40 children, which he couldn't manage to get out anymore.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were eight or 10 adults, including my mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] one of the adults by the name of Mr.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Avien was the cook, for example.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't want to say he was a real cook.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he cooked for us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Zagreb.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother, took over the-- they had a sewing machine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had girls there too, teenager, girls.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they took care of our clothes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They washed our clothes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They ironed our clothes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They mended our clothes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They-- how's this called-- made sweaters and things like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So my mother was in charge of this little group.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The situation was getting worse daily.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The Ustase was getting very pronounced anti-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Groups were taken. 300 Yugoslavian Jews were taken in the age group from, let's say, 16 to 24, and were brought to a camp and just-- we heard later-- are massacred.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were still there and heard about things like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
